claim.claim-text:
4. The power steering system of claim 1, further comprising a frequency suppressor, the frequency suppressor comprising:
a housing having a length, an interior, and first and second internal chambers within the interior, the first internal chamber being in fluid communication with the second internal chamber;
a separator disposed along the length of the housing within the interior of the housing such that the housing and the separator define the first and second internal chambers;
wherein a first portion of the substantially fixed mass of the compressible substance is contained within the first internal chamber, a second portion of the substantially fixed mass of the compressible substance is contained within the second internal chamber, and when the power steering system pressure fluctuates, there is a pressure drop across the separator.
